Driver by Day, Assassin by Night | Full Crime Action Movie | Guns For Hire

Guns For Hire - Beatle, a part time tow truck driver and assassin meets a mysterious, beautiful young woman, with a secret, striking a deadly bargain. The young woman's ex-boyfriend and a killer friend are after her. A kidnap/extortion scheme pits assassin against assassin and brings this deadly game to a mind-bending conclusion.

Stars: Ever Carradine, Michele Hicks, Jeffrey Dean Morgan
